{"tid":383615,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《分歧者》女星因抗爭闖進私人地方入獄要赤裸通櫃，喊叫：根本沒有人權","createTime":"2017-09-01T15:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T16:39:21.000Z","uid":41351,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd36cd7498795ea0f4ae0c193aeae2ceccf997eb","tid":383615,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T15:32:29.000Z","msg":"電影《分歧者》（Divergent）系列美國女星莎蓮活德麗（Shailene Woodley），上年10月喺北達科他州嘅施工地抗議興建輸油管期間被捕，佢當時被鎖上手銬並帶走，事後佢被判緩刑。<br />\n<br />\n事隔近一年，莎蓮接受雜誌《瑪利嘉兒》訪問時，談到當時脫悼衣服被通櫃嘅情況，佢覺得自己好似被困喺籠入面嘅動物，沒有人權：「我要脫掉衣服被搜身，差不多全裸，然後轉身彎腰，他們要檢查我屁股裏有沒有收藏毒品。」莎蓮又話：「當被關在監獄入面，你知道沒有人會救你，當發生火警時，他們都不會開門，你會死於監牢中，就像動物一樣。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170901/57156065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170901%2F57156065&d=NL2wxML9PHmKuXjXFwwIKLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=483b54f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170901%2F57156065&h=a93abaaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170901/57156065</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/01/233153_d9b3e48767eca600e5ed82c5cf32c1d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F01%2F233153_d9b3e48767eca600e5ed82c5cf32c1d2.jpg&h=397cbccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢事件對莎蓮會一番新嘅體會，對於未來會唔會從政，莎蓮就話都唔排除呢個可能：「上年我曾為參議員桑德斯（Bernie Sanders）工作，我就想可能未來幾年後會參選議員，未來的事誰知道？生命很廣闊，而且我還很年輕。」"},{"pid":"b8174d5779f9b3438c55e48ed3adf9d3f29c69ca","tid":383615,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T15:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/01/233631_1a335afae95bbd9bd090fca648eb4e71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F01%2F233631_1a335afae95bbd9bd090fca648eb4e71.jpg&h=ff5196f9&s={S